## 解説

`Stack<char>` に開き括弧を積み、閉じ括弧が来たら一番上 (`Pop`) と対応するか確認します。途中で崩れる、または最後にスタックが空でなければ対応していません。

```csharp
var stack = new Stack<char>();
var pairs = new Dictionary<char, char>();
pairs[')'] = '('; pairs[']'] = '['; pairs['}'] = '{';
bool ok = true;
foreach (char ch in s) {
    if (ch == '(' || ch == '[' || ch == '{') stack.Push(ch);
    else if (stack.Count == 0 || stack.Pop() != pairs[ch]) { ok = false; break; }
}
Console.WriteLine(ok && stack.Count == 0 ? "Yes" : "No");
```

answer_code:
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;

class Program {
    static void Main() {
        string s = Console.ReadLine();
        var stack = new Stack<char>();
        var pairs = new Dictionary<char, char>();
        pairs[')'] = '('; pairs[']'] = '['; pairs['}'] = '{';
        bool ok = true;
        foreach (char ch in s) {
            if (ch == '(' || ch == '[' || ch == '{') stack.Push(ch);
            else if (stack.Count == 0 || stack.Pop() != pairs[ch]) { ok = false; break; }
        }
        Console.WriteLine(ok && stack.Count == 0 ? "Yes" : "No");
    }
}
